        <mxCell id="WUGtP1uMNt8Q-4MS2xaz-41" value="&lt;font&gt;Nomenclature:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;- &lt;b&gt;Selected&lt;/b&gt;: The layout that the user last selected&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;- Displayed: The layout that is currently displayed&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;The user can modify the displayed layout at any time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Actions to support:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;- Load one layout from a list&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;- Save the displayed layout on top of the selected one or another from the list&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;- Warn the user before a layout is lost&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;A layout can be lost in two cases:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;- If another layout overwrites it&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;- If the application is closed while the display layout is different than the selected one&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Fira Code;fontSize=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
